<h2 id="section-top">Oral and Maxillofacial Surgery</h2>
</div>
<div class="col four-sm">
</div>
<div class="col three-sm" id="ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_PlaceHolderMain_contentColumn1">
<div class="box">
<p class="module">
        This Department is managed by  
        <a href="/Services/Trusts/Overview/DefaultView.aspx?id=1843">Lancashire Teaching Hospitals NHS Foundation Trust</a>
</p>
<div class="panel">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<div class="service-locations clear">
<div class="panel edit-box">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<p class="address">RPH Outpatient Clinic<br/>01772 522598</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="panel edit-box">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<p class="address">Ward 4<br/>01772 522498</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="panel">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<div id="imageContent603e07724f034ec7a107f3825b0a4c79">
</div>
<p>Oral and maxillofacial surgery treats conditions and injuries of the head, neck, face, jaws, and mouth.</p>
<p>A full oral and maxillofacial service is provided at Royal Preston Hospital, comprising outpatient, in-patient and day case facilities. All outpatient and day case services are delivered in purposely built accommodation. Inpatient care is provided as part of the ENT ward and the department is supported by a fully equipped maxillofacial laboratory.</p>
<p>At Chorley and South Ribble Hospital, a comprehensive outpatient service for adults and children is provided, together with day case treatment facilities for dento-alveolar and minor oral surgery.</p>
<p>The oral and maxillofacial team includes specialist surgeons, consultant orthodontists, restorative dentistry consultants and laboratory technicians.</p>
<p>Outpatient clinics are held daily.</p>
<p><a href="http://www.lancsteachinghospitals.nhs.uk/oral-and-maxillofacial" target="_blank" title="Oral and Maxillofacial">Click here to view more information on the Lancashire Teaching Hospitals website.</a></p></div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
